trans-unit.source: Dynamically manufactures Web service handler instances, whose type or types implement the <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: 动态生成 Web 服务处理程序实例，其类型实现<xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref>接口。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface establishes the contract that ASP.NET uses to process incoming HTTP Web requests with custom HTTP handlers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>接口建立 ASP.NET 用于处理的传入 HTTP Web 请求以及自定义 HTTP 处理程序的协定。</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>

trans-unit.source: The WebServiceHandlerFactory class produces an instance of an <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> implementation for handling Web service requests.
trans-unit.target: WebServiceHandlerFactory 类生成的实例，实例<xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>实现用于处理 Web 服务请求。</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory"></xref> class.

An <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> that provides references to intrinsic server objects (For example, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request*>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response*>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session*>, and <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Server*>) used to service HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> ，它提供对内部服务器对象的引用 (例如， <> </> *1>， <> </> *1>， <> </> *1>，和<> *1>) 用于 HTTP 请求提供服务。

trans-unit.source: The HTTP data transfer method (GET or POST) that the client uses.
trans-unit.target: HTTP 数据传输客户端使用的方法 （GET 或 POST）。

trans-unit.source: The raw URL of the requested resource.
trans-unit.target: 请求的资源的原始 URL。

trans-unit.source: The file-system path of the requested resource.
trans-unit.target: 请求的资源的文件系统路径。

trans-unit.source: There are no resources associated with a handler instance that the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory> class needs to release.
trans-unit.target: 有没有关联的处理程序资源实例<xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory>类需要释放。</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory>
